@startuml
start
:User accesses list of enrolled courses;
:System presents enrollments and progress status;

if (User Action?) then (Resume Course)
  :User chooses to continue a specific course;
  :System restores learning session at last saved point;
else (Unenroll)
  :User selects option to unenroll from a specific course;
  :System removes the course with its progress from the User's list;
  :System updates the enrollment view;
endif

stop
@enduml
